verbose_text: Compared with the model group, the renal tissue IL-6 level in exenatide-1, exenatide-2 and exenatide-3 groups was significantly decreased, respectively (P < 0.05), and the renal tissue TNF-alpha, hs-CRP and CCL5 levels in exenatide-2 and exenatide-3 groups were significantly decreased, respectively (P < 0.05).
